*.parquet
# Exception: slim seed parquets for the cloud demo's cold start. NOT
# currently in use — Hugging Face Spaces rejects binary files without
# Git LFS setup. Re-enable + add `.gitattributes` LFS tracking if you
# want pre-warmed /providers + /screener on cloud cold start. The
# cloud_seed module is harmless to keep around either way.
# !data/seed/
# !data/seed/**/*.parquet
# !data/seed/**/*.meta

